				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\upmu $$\end{document}s, which is longer than the maximum drift time (5.7 μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
