				\begin{document}$$^{109}$$\end{document}Cd source. The aim is to find the optimum point of operation, in terms of general performance and energy threshold, for a physics run. This optimization is a challenging task as it depends on many factors (the base gas, the quencher and its quantity; and the pressure) and there are few studies in literature on gas properties.

